    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and would make a dependable daily driver or a great project car for someone looking to put in a little work. The exterior shows its age with some noticeable scratches, fading paint on the roof, and a small dent on the rear passenger door. Inside, the upholstery has some visible staining and a small tear in the driver's seat, though all essential electronics remain functional. Mechanically, it runs and drives, but it will likely need a suspension tune-up and new tires in the near future. It\u2019s a solid, honest car that reflects its mileage and years on the road.",
      "price": 22500.0,
