    {
      "id": "optimistic_5_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Looking for a dependable vehicle that\u2019s ready to work as hard as you do? This car is in fair condition and brings plenty of character and life to every journey! While it shows some honest wear and tear from its time on the road, it remains a solid, functional choice for anyone seeking reliable transportation at a great value.",
